  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Key activities at community levels:
1.	Provision of hygiene kits to older women and men and carers (may be same person) 
2.	Dissemination of Age-Friendly educational material on COVID-19
3.	Advocacy on amplifying older people&apos;s voices and ensuring that they are involved in decision-making and that their dignity and autonomy are respected. It is in times of crisis that these are most likely to be ignored or threatened.</narrative>
